    "Erosion of Intellectual FreedomIn times of conflict, the freedom to pursue diverse ideas and engage in critical discourse is often curtailed.",
    "Censorship, ideological control, and persecution of intellectuals and students who voice dissenting opinions become rampant.",
    "Academic autonomy, a cornerstone of higher education, faces severe threats, leading to selfcensorship and stifling of intellectual growth.",
    "The erosion of intellectual freedom amid conflict represents a dire threat to the core principles of higher education.",
    "The erosion of intellectual freedom within higher education during times of conflict threatens the essence of academic inquiry and innovation."
